{
  "stem": "12447.3",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So this continued for a while-- all kinds of situations just to be able to bring in something to the ghettos.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we were able to sell it and eat from it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I remember one time, I even made my way out of the ghetto by-- in-- there used to be a situation when two streetcars would meet right at the gate.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And between the two streetcars, there was a space, maybe like 2 foot wide or so, that nobody would suspect that somebody would go through.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But this situation, I had to wait sometimes for hours until two streetcars would meet right at the gate.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Then I would run through-- between the two streetcars when they stood.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And one policeman would get on it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "The other policeman would get off because they were running in two opposite ways, the, the streetcars.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So between the two street cars, I would run through and run out of the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And by the time the, the street cars would start moving, I would be out of the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And nobody expected somebody to run because it was really dangerous.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You could touch-- you know, you could touch the car with your shoulder.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I guess I was pretty small that I always managed to get out without getting, you know, kind of rubbed off by the streetcar or anything like that.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Except one time, a policeman waited for me on the outside.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When I came on the other side-- he must have seen me running or something.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he started to beat me up with a rubber hose.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I started to run back into the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he kept on running after me, hitting me in the head.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
